tags.name: lrndesign-panelcard
tags.description:
`lrndesign-panelcard`
A LRN element

Attributes:

  * `title` {`string`} - Title of the panel

  * `elevation` {`number`} - Height of the paper.

  * `coloredText` {`boolean`} - Applies the color to the text instead of the background

  * `accent-color` {`string`} - a selected accent-color: grey, red, pink, purple, etc.

  * `dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

  * `colors` - make the default theme dark?
